    "instructions": [
        "In a large pot or Dutch oven, bring the chicken broth and garlic powder to a boil over medium-high heat.",
        "Add the frozen meatballs and the uncooked orzo pasta to the boiling broth.",
        "Reduce the heat to a simmer and cook for 10 to 12 minutes, or until the orzo is tender and the meatballs are heated through.",
        "Stir in the basil pesto and the fresh baby spinach until the spinach has wilted, which should take about 1-2 minutes.",
        "Ladle the soup into bowls and garnish with grated parmesan cheese before serving."
    ],
